{"tid":113501,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙治奧拉莫斯輕鬆入樽向大帝宣戰","createTime":"2017-02-09T04:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T07:54:53.000Z","uid":50847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fadc657f369efcc881b26311a25da64b6ec6601f","tid":113501,"uid":50847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJuwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=aa4fa216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】NBA全明星賽下個周末在新奧爾良舉行，皇家馬德里隊長沙治奧拉莫斯也湊熱鬧，在個人社交媒體上載自己入樽的短片，更點名挑戰「大帝」勒邦占士。<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里是足球壇傳奇球會，其籃球隊亦是傳統勁旅，更是歐聯史上最成功球隊。不時頭頂腳踢助皇馬贏波的隊長沙治奧拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos），原來也擁有不俗的籃球細胞，最近更在個人社交媒體分享了自己打籃球的英姿。<br />\n<br />\n片段所見，下月底將滿31歲生日的拉莫斯身在一個室內場館，雙手持球跑向籃球架，單看其助跑已甚具氣勢。結果拉莫斯不負所望，單腳起跳時未有發生意外而失威；身高6呎的他展示了強勁彈跳力，在他施展單手入樽的一刻，他的頭部貌似與籃板底部成水平線&mdash;&mdash;不過，單看片段，難以判斷該籃框是否按標準定在10呎高的位置。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，拉莫斯輕鬆完成入樽是事實；他對自己的演出似乎亦相當滿意，因而向有「大帝」之稱的NBA巨星勒邦占士下戰書：「為明星賽做好準備。勒邦占士，你能夠做得更好嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/p/BQQLORgFsbV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBQQLORgFsbV&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJuwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0bdc06bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBQQLORgFsbV&h=bf0c97eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/p/BQQLORgFsbV</a>"},{"pid":"2e455af7c2394cd04d00fe40259f413f2b2f95b8","tid":113501,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"串鳩佢走步？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696b7dbdf878e3860f861defa08996a22eb7af53","tid":113501,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"笑鳩foj唔敢玩入樽賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98ecf7ae0c3df07105b3b95b167ee73181dc6cb","tid":113501,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"輕鬆啦玩具"},{"pid":"403d2c35181bf22efc385387d3ed2dc07b89ef8c","tid":113501,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕鬆啦玩具</blockquote><br />\n華布拿都輕鬆入樽啦"},{"pid":"29babde6907a77972f4093799dd9196b192e0230","tid":113501,"uid":4419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>輕鬆啦玩具</blockquote><br />\n華布拿都輕鬆入樽啦</blockquote><br />\n用身體入樽"},{"pid":"df20f772899f9bf7658c8b6fc1985eccb69705be","tid":113501,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.big5.made-in-china.com/37f28j01lCPQrDFMguoH/%E5%8A%A9%E8%B7%B3%E6%9D%BF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.big5.made-in-china.com%2F37f28j01lCPQrDFMguoH%2F%25E5%258A%25A9%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E6%259D%25BF.jpg&h=2cf04425&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67b17fe5d658a837b2c5ead2267a5384877b0d6e","tid":113501,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"得6尺<br />\n仲低過朗度"},{"pid":"c5ee02edb6ac1805d2f3f7b80dc9f38bc8cadeaa","tid":113501,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>串鳩佢走步？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec733b686941945071f6bf25683cb84e063a67e4","tid":113501,"uid":50847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"羅意庭都輕鬆入樽"},{"pid":"e957d597ae3dc152a4bbac69b3dc7f2cc28f6a0d","tid":113501,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"藍波真系好易挽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5eee25443ef433fcf4082c4e5fea6508af735f0","tid":113501,"uid":66651,"lik